          "subtype": "ability",
          "success": "The troop is frightened 1.",
          "text": "If a redcap brigade sees a creature brandish a religious symbol of a deity (which requires an Interact action by that creature) or cast a divine spell while wearing a religious symbol, the troop must attempt a DC 26 Will save. They then become temporarily immune to all brandished religious symbols for 10 minutes.",
          "traits": [
